<p style="text-align: center;"><span>为持续落实疫情防控措施</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span>赛事当天，所有选手参赛前及完赛后</span><span></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span>乘坐地铁须佩戴口罩、</span><span>测体温</span></strong></p>
